Enjoyed Catch A Vibe Part 1? Well get ready for Part 2. Culture & Lovers is the order of the day on this mixtape. Sweet sweet reggae tunes by artist like Tarrus Riley, Richie Spice, Queen Ifrica, veterans like George Nooks, Yami Bolo and Glen Washington, and i even got some fresh fresh tunes by Dutch artists Benaissa and Maikal X aka ShyRock. Don't sleep on them!! You know I had to throw in some sexy tunes by Estelle, John Legend, Da'Ville and Wayne Wonder.

Nuff chat

Download, light a spliff and enjoy... easy!
